schemaVersion: 1
id: book-factory-root
name: Book Factory
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  A complete book-writing OS in a directory. Fill in three placeholders (who you
  are, what the book is about, format + audience), run the bootstrap prompt,
  and a book-coach agent builds your premise sheet, a 12-chapter outline, drafts
  chapter 1, generates cover-art prompts, drafts the back-cover blurb, and
  recommends a publishing path (KDP / IngramSpark / Draft2Digital / hybrid /
  query agent route). Designed for non-fiction; adaptable to memoir.
entry: index.md
